# AI CUP 2026 deliverable .gitignore
# Tracks code + README + reference submission only.
# Data and large caches are user-provided / auto-generated.

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.egg-info/
.Python
*.so

# Data files are now BUNDLED for direct reproducibility (totals ~8 MB):
# - data/train.csv          (主辦提供)
# - data/test_new.csv       (主辦提供)
# - data/test.csv           (主辦 2026-05-21 公告開放 Reference_Only_Old_Test_Data)
# - data/external/shuttleset22/train.csv  (CoachAI Projects, 已開源)

# Cache — now BUNDLED for direct reproducibility (~301 MB total, 52 files):
# - cache/ssl_lstm_encoder_shuttleset22.pt   SSL encoder
# - cache/oof_test_v25a*.npz                 V25-A bag (10 seeds)
# - cache/oof_test_v27*.npz                  V27 bag (10 seeds)
# - cache/oof_test_v38*.npz                  V38 bag (dead-end, for figures)
# - cache/oof_test_tt_shuttlenet*.npz        v1/asym bags (10 seeds each)
# - cache/oof_test_probs.npz                 V3 baseline cascade
# - cache/consensus_microflip/summary.csv    diagnostic summary for fig 6
# Allows judges to verify ensemble + lookup logic in ~25 sec via
# `python scripts/run_full_pipeline.py --skip-ssl --skip-bag`.

# Submission CSVs generated during fresh runs (not the reference)
